parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent failure of headlights can cause reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially when driving at night.
symptoms: Headlights work intermittently
low beam headlights do not work
headlights turn off while driving
headlights turn back on after a short period
voltage meter drops to 12 volts when failure occurs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the Stabili-Trak system can cause the vehicle to lose traction and stability, increasing the risk of accidents and loss of control.
symptoms: The service Stabili-Trak warning light illuminates
the vehicle fails to accelerate as intended
the vehicle experiences intermittent loss of power or acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Battery Drain and Electrical System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The battery drain and electrical system failure can cause the vehicle to stall or leave the driver stranded, increasing the risk of accidents or inconvenience.
symptoms: The battery is drained
the vehicle experiences intermittent electrical system failures
the vehicle stalls or fails to start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the exhaust manifold can cause exhaust fumes to enter the interior of the vehicle, posing a risk to the health and safety of occupants.
symptoms: The exhaust manifold cracks
exhaust fumes enter the interior of the vehicle
the vehicle experiences a loud noise or vibration from the exhaust system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, making it difficult or impossible to accelerate, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: No reverse gear
grinding noise in the first two gears
loss of power
inability to accelerate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, making it difficult or impossible to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Vehicle quits or stalls
inability to restart the vehicle
loss of power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Headlight Drive Module (HDM) can cause both low beam headlights to malfunction, resulting in reduced visibility while driving at night, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Sudden loss of headlights while driving at night
unable to see while driving
headlights do not turn on.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Unidentified Noise from Underneath the Right Passenger's Seat
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unidentified noise from underneath the right passenger's seat can be a sign of a potential underlying issue that can affect the vehicle's safety and performance, although the exact impact is unclear.
symptoms: Abnormal noise emitted from underneath the right passenger's seat
noise recurs multiple times while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall without warning, leading to a loss of power steering and airbag functionality, which can increase the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls without warning
the driver's airbag and steering wheel fail
the frontal airbag and steering wheel position sensor need to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Contaminated brake fluid can cause the brakes to lock up, leading to a loss of vehicle control, which can increase the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle slows down on its own
the brakes lock up
the service stabltrk light comes on
the brakes make a noise similar to a flat tire.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the brakes to lock up, leading to a loss of vehicle control, which can increase the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle slows down on its own
the brakes lock up
the service stabltrk light comes on
the brakes make a noise similar to a flat tire.
